<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><subLeg xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0 https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/schemas/hklm.xsd" xml:lang="en"><meta><docName>Cap. 358 sub. leg. X</docName><docType>cap</docType><docNumber>358X</docNumber><docStatus>In effect</docStatus><dc:identifier>/hk/cap358X!en</dc:identifier><dc:date>2024-08-18</dc:date><dc:subject>legislation</dc:subject><dc:language>en</dc:language><dc:publisher>DoJ</dc:publisher><dc:rights>the Government of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region</dc:rights></meta><main xml:lang="en" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0 https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/schemas/hklm.xsd"><docTitle id="ID_1438403056256_001" name="shortTitle" reason="inEffect" status="operational" temporalId="shortTitle" startPeriod="2019-12-12">Statement
                                    of Water Quality Objectives (North Western Water Control
                                    Zone)</docTitle><enactingFormula role="empoweringSection">(<ref href="/hk/cap358/s5">Cap.
                                                358,
                                                section 5</ref>)</enactingFormula><sourceNote>(Enacting provision omitted—<ref href="hk/2019/er6">E.R. 6 of 2019</ref>)</sourceNote><enactingFormula role="empoweringSection">
                                    <marker role="blank-line"></marker>
                                    <marker role="blank-line"></marker>
                        </enactingFormula><commencementNote>[28 February 1992]</commencementNote><sourceNote>(Format changes—<ref href="hk/2019/er6">E.R. 6 of 2019</ref>)</sourceNote><section id="ID_1438403056256_003" name="s1" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2019-12-12" status="operational" temporalId="s1"><num value="1">1.</num><content>The water quality objectives set out in column 1 of the <ref>Schedule</ref> are established for those parts of the North Western Water Control Zone set opposite those water quality objectives in column 2.</content></section><section id="ID_1438403056271_001" name="s2" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2024-08-18" status="operational" temporalId="s2"><num value="2">2.</num><leadIn>In this Statement—</leadIn><def name="BathingBeachSubzone"><leadIn><term>Bathing
                    Beach
                Subzone</term>
                    (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">泳灘分區</term>) means—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438412071477_019" name="a" temporalId="s2_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>a bathing beach that is specified in the <ref>Fourth Schedule</ref> to the Public Health and Municipal Services Ordinance (<ref href="/hk/cap132">Cap. 132</ref>) and situated in the North Western Water Control Zone; and</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438412071477_027" name="b" temporalId="s2_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>the bathing beach at Lung Kwu Tan, which is delineated on a plan marked
                    NWWCZ/LK, signed by the Secretary for Planning, Environment and Lands on 6
                    November 1991 and deposited in the Land
                        Registry;<inline class="width_3"> </inline><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1993/8">8 of 1993 s.
                            30</ref>; <ref href="/hk/2024/21">21 of 2024 s.
                        78</ref>)</sourceNote></content></paragraph></def><def name="CastlePeakBaySubzone"><term>Castle
                Peak Bay
            Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">青山灣分區</term>) means an area delineated as such on the
            Map;</def><def name="Map"><term>Map</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">地圖</term>) means a series of maps comprising 5 sheets
            and marked from NWWCZ 1 to NWWCZ 5, signed by the Secretary for Planning, Environment
            and Lands on 6 November 1991 and deposited in the Land
                Registry;<inline class="width_3"> </inline><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1993/8">8 of 1993 s.
                30</ref>; <ref href="/hk/2024/21">21 of 2024 s. 78</ref>)</sourceNote></def><def name="MarineWaters"><term>marine
                waters</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">海洋水域</term>) means all waters below the high water mark
            within the boundary of the North Western Water Control Zone;</def><def name="OtherInlandWaters"><term>other
                inland
            waters</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">其他內陸水域</term>) means inland waters other than those in
            the Tuen Mun (A), Tuen Mun (B) and Tuen Mun (C) Subzones;</def><def name="SecondaryContactRecreationSubzone"><term>Secondary
                Contact Recreation
            Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">次級接觸康樂活動分區</term>) means an area delineated as such on
            the Map, except where the area is more specifically designated as a bathing beach;</def><def name="TuenMunASubzone"><term>Tuen
                Mun (A)
            Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">屯門(A)分區</term>) means that part of the catchment of the
            Tuen Mun River which is delineated and marked TM(A) on the Map;</def><def name="TuenMunBSubzone"><term>Tuen
                Mun (B)
            Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">屯門(B)分區</term>) means that part of the catchment of the
            Tuen Mun River which is delineated and marked TM(B) on the Map;</def><def name="TuenMunCSubzone"><term>Tuen
                Mun (C)
            Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">屯門(C)分區</term>) means that part of the catchment of the
            Tuen Mun River which is delineated and marked TM(C) on the Map;</def><def name="WaterGatheringGroundSubzone"><term>Water
                Gathering Ground
            Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">集水地區分區</term>) means an area delineated as such on the
            Map.</def></section><schedule id="ID_1438403056287_001" name="sch0" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2019-12-12" status="operational" temporalId="sch0"><num value="0">Schedule</num><note class="align_right" role="crossReferences" type="inline">[<ref href="/hk/cap358X/s1">s. 1</ref>]</note><text>
            
            
            <table xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" frame="void" width="446" class="repeat_header">
                <col width="5%"></col>
                <col width="7%"></col>
